<h1><i class="fa fa-info-circle"></i>Viewing Chat Info</h1>

<ol class="breadcrumb">
	<li><a href="#help"><i class="fa fa-question-circle"></i>Help</a></li>
	<li><a href="#help/sharing-messages"><i class="fa fa-comment"></i>Sharing Messages</a></li>
	<li><i class="fa fa-info-circle"></i>Viewing Chat Info</li>
</ol>

<div class="content">
	<p>You can view information associated with a particular chat conversation, including the create date, current members, and invitations. </p>

	<ol>
		<li>
			<h2><i class="fa fa-info-circle"></i>Show Info</h2>
			<p>In order to show the information associated with a particular chat, select a chat and then click "Show Info" on the File Menu.  This will display the Chat Info dialog box. </p>

			<div class="figure">
				<img class="dropdown menu" src="images/help/sharing-messages/viewing-chat-info/show-info-menu-item@2x.png" />
				<div class="caption">"Show Info" on the File Menu</div>
			</div>

			<div class="tip well">
				<h3><span class="icon"><i class="fa fa-lightbulb"></i></span>Tip</h3><p>You can quickly view chat info using the keyboard shortcut: command or control + I.</p>
			</div>
		</li>

		<li>
			<h2><i class="fa fa-comments"></i>Chat Info Dialog Box</h2>
			<p>The chat info dialog box contains a number of tabs showing different aspects of information about the chat conversation. </p>

			<ol>
				<li>
					<h3><span class="icon"><i class="fa fa-info-circle"></i></span>General</h3>
					<p>This tab contains general information about a chat. </p>

					<div class="figure">
						<a href="images/help/sharing-messages/viewing-chat-info/chat-info.png" target="_blank" class="lightbox" title="Chat General Info"><img class="dialog" src="images/help/sharing-messages/viewing-chat-info/chat-info.png" /></a>
						<div class="caption">Chat General Info</div>
					</div>
				</li>

				<li>
					<h3><span class="icon"><i class="fa fa-user"></i></span>Members</h3>
					<p>This tab contains the current chat members.</p>

					<div class="figure">
						<a href="images/help/sharing-messages/viewing-chat-info/chat-members-info.png" target="_blank" class="lightbox" title="Chat Members Info"><img class="dialog" src="images/help/sharing-messages/viewing-chat-info/chat-members-info.png" /></a>
						<div class="caption">Chat Members Info</div>
					</div>
				</li>

				<li>
					<h3><span class="icon"><i class="fa fa-envelope"></i></span>Invitations</h3>
					<p>This tab contains invitations about the chat invitations that have been sent.</p>

					<div class="figure">
						<a href="images/help/sharing-messages/viewing-chat-info/chat-invitations-info.png" target="_blank" class="lightbox" title="Chat Invitations Info"><img class="dialog" src="images/help/sharing-messages/viewing-chat-info/chat-invitations-info.png" /></a>
						<div class="caption">Chat Invitations Info</div>
					</div>
				</li>
			</ol>
		</li>
	</ol>
</div>